            "content": [
              {
                "type": "output_text",
                "text": "I can’t access or show *actual* sales records from the data sources available to me right now—there isn’t any sales data present in the systems I can query【6:0†source】.\n\nIf you tell me **where your sales records live** (e.g., the Fabric workspace dataset/table name, database, or file location) and what you want (summary, schema/fields, KPIs, anomalies, etc.), I can help analyze them.  \n\nIn the meantime, if you meant “sales records” in general (not a specific dataset), tell me your industry (retail/SaaS/services) and I’ll outline the typical structure/fields and common reports.",
